SUMMARY:Opening Night Kick-Off
LOCATION:Mills Hardware\, 95 King St E\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: HFTco (Hamilton)\nContent warnings: Could include matu
 re content\, sexual content\, coarse language\, and/or violence\nIt's the 
 party that kicks it all off! A night full of fun\, friends\, and a few sur
 prises\, the Kick-Off features this year's Fringe artists pitching YOU the
 ir shows – in just 90 seconds or less! It's a great way to see what's ha
 ppening on our Fringe stages this year\, and to decide which shows you wan
 t to check out.\nGeneral Admission: FREE\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/even
 ts/opening-night-kick-off/
