SUMMARY:Awake and Dreaming
LOCATION:The Westdale\, 1014 King St W\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: SJMD (Hamilton\, ON)\nContent warnings: Depictions of 
 family conflict\nGenre: Musical/Concert/Opera\nBased on the award-winning 
 novel by Kit Pearson\, Awake and Dreaming follows Theo\, a child living in
  poverty with her young\, irresponsible mother Rae in Vancouver. When Theo
  meets the seemingly perfect Kaldor family on the ferry and desperately wi
 shes she could be part of them. The magic that follows teaches her about f
 amily\, stories\, and the beautiful imperfections of life.\nGeneral Admiss
 ion: $14\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/events/awake-and-dreaming/
URL:https://hftco.ca/events/awake-and-dreaming/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
