LOCATION:The Players’ Guild of Hamilton\, 80 Queen St S\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: Xenoproductions (Hamilton\, ON)\nContent warnings: Coa
 rse Language\nGenre: Theatre—Drama\nWhen Syl’s marriage goes the way o
 f the dodo\, best friend Kirsten suggests a road trip\, just like in their
  old college days. But they’re not the same women they were back then\, 
 and the addition of a third wheel in the car threatens to upend the friend
 ship\, and maybe a little more.\nGeneral Admission: $14\nMore info: https:
 //hftco.ca/events/spooning-the-great-bear-by-the-light-of-the-moon/
