SUMMARY:CANCELLED — WOLFE (formerly Some of This is True)
LOCATION:The Gasworks\, 141 Park St N\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:*** THIS PERFORMANCE IS CANCELLED ***\nCompany: Ravora Producti
 ons (Toronto\, ON)\nContent warnings: Sexual Content\, Coarse Language\, V
 iolence\, Themes of sexual harrasment and or abuse\nGenre: Theatre—Drama
 \nWritten and performed by award winning theatre artist Diana Bentley (Hed
 da Gabler\, Frontier\, Handmaid's Tale) this one woman show is a thrilling
  one hour ride that will leave your heart racing and your mind reeling. Wh
 en Sandra Martin\, the Artistic Director of Canada's National Theatre find
 s herself at the centre of a massive scandal\, she is forced to unravel th
 e events of her career and a relationship with her favourite and most este
 emed actress.\nGeneral Admission: $14\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/events/
 some-of-this-is-true/
URL:https://hftco.ca/events/some-of-this-is-true/
