SUMMARY:1 Million Served- Years Well Waitressed
LOCATION:The Staircase | Elaine May\, 27 Dundurn St N\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: Outport Productions (Hamilton\, ON)\nContent warnings:
  Sexual Content\, Coarse Language\nGenre: Storytelling/Solo Show\nAfter 35
  years of waitressing\, Wanda’s seen it all—first dates\, last chances
 \, celebrations\, heartbreaks\, and everything in between. Now\, she’s s
 tepping out from behind the table and into the spotlight with a one-woman 
 show that serves up stories rich with life lessons\, humour\, and her unde
 niable Newfoundland charm.\nGeneral Admission: $14\nMore info: https://hft
 co.ca/events/1-million-served-years-well-waitressed/
URL:https://hftco.ca/events/1-million-served-years-well-waitressed/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
