 e\nContent warnings: Audience Participation\, Coarse Language\nGenre: Thea
 tre—Comedy\, Sketch Comedy/Improv\, Storytelling/Solo Show\nStep inside 
 a chaotic golf course kitchen where tempers run hot and survival is the on
 ly goal. Into the Swing of Things is a fast paced one man show that brings
  to life a seasoned cook and an unpredictable dishwasher through high ener
 gy character shifts and physical storytelling. Darkly funny and deeply rea
