SUMMARY:A Seance Spectacular with the Mystical Medium Wolf Sisters from the
  Great White North
LOCATION:Mills Hardware\, 95 King St E\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: Ghosts Are Everywhere (Hamilton/Toronto\, ON)\nSpecial
 : Mask-Mandatory Performance\nContent warnings: Audience Participation\nGe
 nre: Theatre—Comedy\, Theatre—Drama\nTwo Victorian spiritualist sister
 s invite you to a seance. But what happens when someone tries to expose th
 eir act as a sham just as the spirits make their first move? Comedians Car
 ly Anna Billings (The Second City Toronto) and Cecilia O'Grady will take y
 ou back in time. Part comedy\, part scare\, this 60-minute show created an
 d performed by these 'hilarious hosts' (Common Ground Arts\, Edmonton) is 
 sure to deliver you a spine-tinglingly silly spirit-filled story.\nGeneral
  Admission: $14\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/events/a-seance-spectacular-w
 ith-the-mystical-medium-wolf-sisters-from-the-great-white-north/
URL:https://hftco.ca/events/a-seance-spectacular-with-the-mystical-medium-w
 olf-sisters-from-the-great-white-north/
