 s: Sexual Content\, Coarse Language\, discussion of sexual assault & misog
 yny\, religious criticism\, and partial nudity\nGenre: Theatre—Drama\nWh
 en a banker walks into a brothel and pays for an hour with the most expens
 ive woman\, what he gets is not what either of them expected. Witty\, furi
