 rnings: Sexual Content\, Coarse Language\nGenre: Theatre—Comedy\, Puppet
 ry\, Storytelling/Solo Show\nWhat do you do when your most embarrassing st
 ories are also your best ones? You get a puppet to tell them for you. Felt
  Cute\, Might Overshare Later! is a solo comedy confessional where Kristi 
 and her felt alter-ego revisit a lifetime of cringeworthy\, 100% true disa
 sters\, from childhood catastrophes to romantic misfires so spectacular th
 ey almost don't seem real. Funny\, weird\, and sneakily heartfelt. The pup
