SUMMARY:The Last Hornblower
LOCATION:Centre For Talking Arts\, 154 James St S\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: Live the Questions (Guelph\, ON)\nGenre: Storytelling/
 Solo Show\nDo not ask for whom the horn blows. Nobody on the Grande Torino
  did. The greatest soccer team Italy ever assembled simply rolled up their
  sleeves and confronted their opponents. Even the gods fought their demons
  when the horn bellowed from the deep at Ragnarok. We are never powerless.
  Never alone. Through the ageless art of storytelling\, we’ll sound the 
 horn that inspires us to step up when time is always against us.\nGeneral 
 Admission: $14\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/events/the-last-hornblower/
