 formance\nGenre: Storytelling/Solo Show\nDo not ask for whom the horn blow
 s. Nobody on the Grande Torino did. The greatest soccer team Italy ever as
 sembled simply rolled up their sleeves and confronted their opponents. Eve
 n the gods fought their demons when the horn bellowed from the deep at Rag
 narok. We are never powerless. Never alone. Through the ageless art of sto
 rytelling\, we’ll sound the horn that inspires us to step up when time i
 s always against us.\nGeneral Admission: $14\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/
 events/the-last-hornblower/
