DESCRIPTION:Company: Fake Cult Productions (Hamilton\, ON)\nContent warning
 s: Contents may blow your mind.\nGenre: Theatre—Comedy\, Theatre—Drama
 \, Storytelling/Solo Show\nWhat happens when a hyper-rational\, left-brain
 ed\, and very logical philosopher encounters the psychedelic? He over-corr
 ects and finds himself in a radically unscheduled and improvised life of a
 n artist. Complete artistic freedom however does not lead to great works. 
 He needs to schedule his improv. Unable to submit to any entity that tells
  him what to do\, he decides to create his own cult to live well and escap
 e the nihilistic absurdity of the universe.\nGeneral Admission: $14\nMore 
