 ppens when someone tries to expose their act as a sham just as the spirits
  make their first move? Comedians Carly Anna Billings (The Second City Tor
 onto) and Cecilia O'Grady will take you back in time. Part comedy\, part s
 care\, this 60-minute show created and performed by these 'hilarious hosts
