 s of a group of adults who met in an acting class. As they navigate nerves
 \, vulnerability\, and unexpected joy\, they discover the power of steppin
 g outside their comfort zones. Warm\, relatable\, and uplifting\, this sho
 w is a celebration of creativity\, connection\, and the courage to try som
 ething new—at any stage of life.\nGeneral Admission: $14\nMore info: htt
 ps://hftco.ca/events/intro-to-adult-acting/
