 : Relaxed Performance\nContent warnings: Audience Participation\nGenre: Th
 eatre—Comedy\, Theatre—Drama\nTwo Victorian spiritualist sisters invit
 e you to a seance. But what happens when someone tries to expose their act
  as a sham just as the spirits make their first move? Comedians Carly Anna
  Billings (The Second City Toronto) and Cecilia O'Grady will take you back
  in time. Part comedy\, part scare\, this 60-minute show created and perfo
 rmed by these 'hilarious hosts' (Common Ground Arts\, Edmonton) is sure to
  deliver you a spine-tinglingly silly spirit-filled story.\nGeneral Admiss
 ion: $14\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/events/a-seance-spectacular-with-the
 -mystical-medium-wolf-sisters-from-the-great-white-north/
