  Verified follows a trans woman and sex worker who fought back against pol
 ice abuse - and won. Using court transcripts and archival records\, this b
 old new play blends documentary theatre\, courtroom drama\, and biting hum
 our to expose how so-called “procedure” can be used to justify harm.\n
 General Admission: $14\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/events/victoria-schnei
 der-verified/
