DESCRIPTION:Company: BULL & BLOSSOM INITIATIVE (Hamilton\, ON)\nContent war
 nings: Audience Participation\, Sexual Content\, Coarse Language\nGenre: T
 heatre—Comedy\nCome hungry\, leave laughing. First Bite to Last Laugh br
 ings Hamilton’s local food scene together with a vibrant\, diverse comed
 y lineup for a night that hits every sense. Think cookout energy\; curated
  local eats\, plates in your lap\, and big laughs on stage. It’s a casua
 l\, communal experience where the atmosphere is just as rich as what’s o
 n your plate.\nGeneral Admission: $14\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/events/
 first-bite-to-last-laugh/
URL:https://hftco.ca/events/first-bite-to-last-laugh/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
