DESCRIPTION:Company: Solo Chicken Productions (Fredericton\, NB)\nContent w
 arnings: Due to the improvised nature of the show\, TILT can't provide spe
 cific warnings. Audience should be prepared for the possibility of loud so
 unds and sudden lighting effects.\nGenre: Theatre—Comedy\, Sketch Comedy
 /Improv\nA couple’s rocky domestic life takes a turn when a shocking sec
 ret comes to light. What secret? You decide! TILT begins as a fully script
 ed piece of movement theatre that is thrown into an improvised tailspin! W
 hat follows is a totally improvised continuation of the story\, complete w
 ith improvised technical design and new characters\, and concluding with t
 he couple’s ultimate decision... Have their relationship torn apart or s
 tick it out\, despite it all?\nGeneral Admission: $14\nMore info: https://
 hftco.ca/events/tilt/
