SUMMARY:It’s A Live Mixtape
LOCATION:The Westdale\, 1014 King St W\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: Skywav Broadcasting (Hamilton\, ON)\nContent warnings:
  Audience Participation\, Sexual Content\, Coarse Language\nGenre: Musical
 /Concert/Opera\nThe Skywav Broadcasting crew is putting on a show! Unfortu
 nately\, everyone is sick and disabled. Join Onglish (Brett Klassen)\, a D
 J/producer as he crafts a live mixtape: Side A sees rappers Messy (Kitoko 
 Mai) and Tarek Funk bring charged political raps about disability and futu
 rism\, while side B is a dance-y Electro-Mandé-Soul set by singer/songwri
 ter Eye-Sha. This summer\, a delusional love is on the air.\nGeneral Admis
 sion: $14\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/events/its-a-live-mixtape/
